parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the timing chain can cause the engine to stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded. It can also cause damage to the engine and other components, resulting in costly repairs.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the turbocharger can cause the engine to lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded. It can also cause damage to the engine and other components, resulting in costly repairs.

and smoke is present from the exhaust.
